snippet.title: Boom Slingers Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Boom Slingers is a new explosive turn-based action game! Battle with other Slingers. Collect battle cards, characters and emotes. Fight your way up the seasonal leaderboards.

Unlock and upgrade over 50 different weapons and over 70 different Slingers. Battle in quick-to-play 1v1 battles in maps that change daily and participate in weekend events every weekend.

Collect cards, characters, gems and coins by playing games and progressing through the galaxies!

Join our Boom Slingers discord:
https://discord.gg/boomslingers

Download on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tuokio.boomslingers&hl=en&gl=US

Download on Apple AppStore:
https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/boom-slingers/id1507936643

Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/boomslingers

TikTok:
https://www.tiktok.com/@boomslingersofficial

Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/BoomSlingers
